{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/portfolio/shoolu-product-api/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"4d938a06-2cca-5516-bfc2-f1e687cbfc5d","html":"<p>BigCommerce has their <a href=\"https://github.com/bigcommerce/stencil-cli\">Stencil Framework</a> to build themes for their platform. I've extensively customized just about everything I can on Shoolu's Stencil Theme, but one massive thing is missing:</p>\n<h3 id=\"you-cant-query-specific-products-to-display\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#you-cant-query-specific-products-to-display\" aria-label=\"you cant query specific products to display permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>You can't query specific products to display</h3>\n<p>I'm sure there's some kind of technical explanation for the lack of querying ability, but I needed it, <em>so I built it</em>.</p>\n<p>By using the <code class=\"language-text\">bigcommerce-php-api</code> wrapper for the BigCommerce API I was able to build my own Endpoint. Send it a Category or Brand ID, a count, whether to search sub-categories, and a few other parameters and it'll spit back a list of product IDs.</p>\n<p>Back on the stencil theme frontend I would query the Product API, get the list of IDs back, then use BigCommerce's <code class=\"language-text\">stencil-utlils</code> library to query the individual product data and add it to the Product Card template.</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#next-steps\" aria-label=\"next steps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Next Steps</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Rebuild the whole project with Node/Express for a more responsive API</li>\n<li>Have the API itself return the product card/data/whatever instead of relying on the <code class=\"language-text\">stencil-utils</code> library.</li>\n<li>Package the server code up in such a way that's shareable.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"but-what-about-graphql\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#but-what-about-graphql\" aria-label=\"but what about graphql permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>But What About GraphQL?</h2>\n<p>BigCommerce recently launched their GraphQL \"Storefront API\". Their GraphQL does offer what I need to make this happen, but they have no way to only query products that are in stock. You'd call <code class=\"language-text\">getProductsByBrand(\"BRAND\")</code> and it returns everything in that Brand, regardless of current inventory.</p>\n<p>Apparently this <em>is</em> something BigCommerce is working on, but as of writing it's not a viable option.</p>","wordCount":{"words":243},"frontmatter":{"title":"Shoolu Product API","description":"Filling Gaps In BigCommerce","color":"#0fb681","date":"January 07, 2020","tags":["PHP","AJAX","BigCommerce","E-Commerce"],"images":[{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/0505c/shoolu-product-grid.png","srcSet":"/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/2376d/shoolu-product-grid.png 200w,\n/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/1433e/shoolu-product-grid.png 400w,\n/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/0505c/shoolu-product-grid.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/81dbe/shoolu-product-grid.webp 200w,\n/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/450f1/shoolu-product-grid.webp 400w,\n/static/28d89b9aef1e628ceef1286c8d30a3b1/99ec4/shoolu-product-grid.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":800,"height":667}}}],"logo":{"extension":"svg","publicURL":"/static/20ed27871795831b373cdedc681abde9/shoolu-logo.svg"}},"fields":{"slug":"/portfolio/shoolu-product-api/","collection":"portfolio","externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out Â»","unlisted":false}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/portfolio/shoolu-product-api/","related":[{"fields":{"slug":"/portfolio/dreamclub-united/","collection":"portfolio","published":true},"frontmatter":{"color":"#222","title":"Dreamclub United","description":"LA Non Profit","tags":["E-Commerce","WordPress","Non Profit"],"logo":{"publicURL":"/static/b274658326547f38d3b542a9e616168a/Dream-Club-Logo.png"}}},{"fields":{"slug":"/portfolio/bottle-rocket-hot-sauce-co/","collection":"portfolio","published":true},"frontmatter":{"color":"#e94939","title":"Bottle Rocket Hot Sauce","description":"Pre Sale Shopify Theme","tags":["Shopify","E-Commerce","Animation"],"logo":{"publicURL":"/static/3079